sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant AuthServer
    participant Resource
    User->>App: Login request
    App->>AuthServer: Validate credentials
    AuthServer-->>App: Access token
    App-->>User: Login success
    User->>App: Get data
    App->>Resource: Fetch with token
    Resource-->>App: Data
    App-->>User: Display data
